<h1 id="privacypolicy">Privacy Policy</h1>

<p class="lede">Detention Logs is committed to protecting the privacy of visitors to our site. Where we do collect information about our users, we want them to know about it and understand how and why we use it—so there are no&nbsp;surprises.</p>

<h2 id="googleanalytics">Google Analytics</h2>

<p>Detention Logs collects aggregate information about the use of our site to help us improve our work and measure its impact. This information helps us understand for example; how many visits a particular page has had, roughly where our visits come from geographically, how search engines are directing people to our site, and what pages are popular on social media. The information collected does not include any personal information other than users’ IP addresses. We will never disclose any IP address information, or information that could be used to identify an individual or group of users.</p>

